This is a simple and barebones program for a line-following robot. The speed and turning logic need to be fine-tuned for your specific setup. If you're using an ultrasonic sensor, instead of ‘lightSensorValue,’ use the delay between sending the signal and receiving the echo to determine if the robot is on the line or off-line (obstacle ahead or line missing).

